Ghana’s Opposition May Take Speaker to Court, Graphic Reports

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-06-28T10:34:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/ghana-s-opposition-may-take-speaker-to-court-graphic-reports.html
Ghana ’s opposition may take
parliamentary speaker, Joyce Bamford-Addo, to court for
dismissing an amendment to an oil law passed this year, Graphic
reported.  Bamford-Addo ruled against a proposal to allocate 10
percent of oil revenue from the Jubilee oil field to the
development of the Western Region, the Accra-based  newspaper 
said, citing Osei Kyei-Mensah-Bonsu, an opposition leader.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 